version_description: I combined chords and tabs, corrected and improved them and make it all simple to read and play.
Has the passing chords included, has the correct Chorus chords and correct lyrics.
Red Hot Chili Peppers - Dark Necessities Link https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qJ_Tw0w3lLA No Capo.
Didn't see any tabs with these chords. Played this around a few times and sounds correct to me.
The recorded version of "Encore" is in Ab minor. These are the chords you can strum along with the recorded song and chord changes that correspond with the timing of the lyrics.
This version is precisely what is played in the original record from the album.
